** What is Next

  1.0 is a foundation, not a finish line. The focus now shifts to:

  - *Content quality*: richer content schemas, cross-file validation, link checking, and built-in image
    optimization
  - *DX tooling*: interactive lith init with project templates, better error suggestions, and
    smoother onboarding
  - *Asset bundling and cache fingerprinting*: combine JS and CSS files; add content hashes to
    filenames for aggressive cache busting (minification is already in place!)
  - *Built-in search via plugin*: full-text search backed by ripgrep in WASM or a similarly
    performant approach, distributed through the existing plugin system

  Have ideas? {https://github.com/norgolith/core/issues/new}[Open an issue] or
  {https://discord.gg/T6EgTAX7ht}[join us on Discord].

** Full Changelog

  The complete changelog is available on GitHub:
  {https://github.com/norgolith/core/releases/tag/norgolith-v1.0.0}[v1.0.0 Release]

  It includes 53 commits across 66 files, with 6650 lines added and 4533 removed.
